|CKBDistract: Throw Your Voice, Keep Your Teeth|000

Syntax: distract [foe]

At Rank 3 and Misdirection 2, place an insult, warning, or deeply personal
observation just over your foe's shoulder. The interruption spoils their
concentration. With deep enough Misdirection, the mark may briefly disengage
while searching for the imaginary speaker.

A foe who refuses the bait still costs you the effort and recovery time.
